{"tid":747625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【書展開鑼】前助理「張達明」出書揭佔中內幕　鄭宇碩：他盜取「我的檔案」","createTime":"2018-07-18T13:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T10:55:09.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4158cd06b8ca60f71e7f177bce7ce806ee13a2c9","tid":747625,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"書展今早開鑼，一名叫做張達明的人，舉辦新書《何為證據：揭露香港亂象的幕後黑手》簽名會，稱該書要踢爆2014年由鄭宇碩牽頭的真普選聯盟和佔中運動，「勾結外國勢力禍港」的幕後證據。鄭宇碩接受本報查詢時確認，這位張達明曾做過他的助理，並曾在他的電腦「我的檔案」非法盜取資料。鄭宇碩強調，真普聯並沒有接受海外組織捐款，資金「來來去去是本地幾個人」。<br />\n<br />\n張達明今日在香港新華書城出版有限公司攤位為新書舉行簽名會，獲保衛香港運動成員到場支持。張達明稱，在城市大學當代中國研究計畫做高級研究助理，上司是鄭宇碩教授，指鄭參與華人民主書院、真普聯、真普選聯盟和民主動力等團體活動，因此他曾協助鄭處理很多相關檔案，他便靠這些檔案內容寫書。張達明又指控真普聯，曾接受美國國家民主基金之下美國國際民主研究院(National Democratic Institute for International Affairs, NDI）的捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180718/s00001/1531905961639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180718%2Fs00001%2F1531905961639&d=qask72%2FD4s3iSAoRDr6ZGzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=995c1c69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180718%2Fs00001%2F1531905961639&h=0311eee9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180718/s00001/1531905961639</a>"},{"pid":"ce7d41060c5e2cb68a5672cac79fc4f0ad143671","tid":747625,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bf0f1aa0e37a6dde1e5527c64f8b6abbfa90c0","tid":747625,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de84970749468b8e753a1f1a2a5895c71ee17811","tid":747625,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:51